# Pytorch Image Classification

This repository contains code for image classification using Pytorch.

## Data Set

The data set used is [CIFAR-10](https://www.cs.toronto.edu/~kriz/cifar.html), which consists of images of size `32x32` in `10` classes.

## Model Architecture

The model architecture is based on [ResNet](https://arxiv.org/abs/1512.03385).

## Training Details

The model was trained on a single GPU with batch size `128` and learning rate `5e-4`.

## Results

The model achieved an accuracy of `93.9%` on the test set.
